# Privacy Policy for KeepWise

**Last Updated: March 16, 2026**

## Introduction

KeepWise ("we", "our", or "the app") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our expense tracking application.

## Our Privacy Commitment

**KeepWise is a 100% offline, privacy-first application. We do NOT collect, transmit, or share any of your personal data.**

## Information We Do NOT Collect

- ❌ No personal information
- ❌ No financial data transmission
- ❌ No usage analytics
- ❌ No crash reports sent to servers
- ❌ No advertising identifiers
- ❌ No location data
- ❌ No contact information
- ❌ No device identifiers sent externally
- ❌ No third-party tracking

## Data Storage

### Local Storage Only
All your data is stored exclusively on your device using:
- **iOS Keychain** - For secure PIN storage (encrypted with AES-256)
- **AsyncStorage** - For transaction data (local device storage)
- **Device Secure Storage** - For encryption keys

### What Data is Stored Locally
The following information is stored ONLY on your device:
1. **PIN** - Your 6-digit authentication PIN (encrypted)
2. **Transactions** - Your expense records including:
   - Amount
   - Currency
   - Category
   - Date
   - Optional description/notes
3. **Settings** - Your app preferences:
   - Default currency
   - App configuration

### Data Security
- All sensitive data is encrypted using AES-256 encryption
- Encryption keys are stored in iOS Keychain (hardware-backed secure storage)
- PIN is never stored in plain text
- Data is protected by your device's security features

## Data Access

### Who Can Access Your Data
- **Only You** - Your data is accessible only on your device
- **No Remote Access** - We cannot access your data
- **No Cloud Sync** - Data never leaves your device
- **No Backups to Our Servers** - We don't have servers

### Device Access
The app requires the following device permissions:
- **Keychain Access** - To securely store your encrypted PIN
- **Local Storage** - To save your transaction data on device

The app does NOT require or request:
- ❌ Internet/Network access
- ❌ Camera access (permission listed but not used)
- ❌ Photo library access (permission listed but not used)
- ❌ Location services
- ❌ Contacts
- ❌ Microphone

*Note: Some permissions appear in Info.plist due to React Native dependencies but are not actively used by the app.*

## Data Sharing

**We do NOT share your data with anyone because we never have access to it.**

- No data is transmitted over the internet
- No data is sold to third parties
- No data is shared with advertisers
- No data is used for analytics
- No data is sent to cloud services

## Data Retention

- **Your Control** - You control all your data
- **Local Only** - Data remains on your device until you delete it
- **App Deletion** - Uninstalling the app permanently deletes all data
- **No Remote Copies** - We don't keep copies of your data

## Data Deletion

You can delete your data at any time:
1. **Individual Transactions** - Delete any transaction in the app
2. **All Data** - Use "Clear All Data" in Settings
3. **Complete Removal** - Uninstall the app to remove all data

## Children's Privacy

KeepWise does not collect any data from anyone, including children under 13. The app can be safely used by users of all ages as it operates entirely offline.

## Third-Party Services

KeepWise does NOT use any third-party services, including:
- No analytics services (Google Analytics, Firebase, etc.)
- No advertising networks
- No crash reporting services
- No cloud storage services
- No social media integrations
- No payment processors

## Encryption

We use industry-standard encryption to protect your data:
- **AES-256 Encryption** - Military-grade encryption for PIN storage
- **iOS Keychain** - Hardware-backed secure storage
- **Device-Specific Keys** - Unique encryption key per device
- **NIST Compliant** - Follows NIST FIPS 197 standards

## Your Rights

Since all data is stored locally on your device, you have complete control:
- ✅ **Right to Access** - View all your data in the app
- ✅ **Right to Modify** - Edit any transaction
- ✅ **Right to Delete** - Remove any or all data
- ✅ **Right to Export** - Export data to CSV (feature available in app)
- ✅ **Right to Portability** - Your data is yours to keep

## Data Breaches

Since we don't collect or store data on servers, there is no risk of:
- Server breaches
- Data leaks
- Unauthorized access to our systems
- Mass data exposure

Your data security depends entirely on your device security.

